<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-11-15T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-11-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="695" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d695">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">123 M 956/282</note>
                            <head>
                                <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss>
                                    to Mr. <persName type="to">Robert D. Murphy</persName>
                                </hi>
                            </head>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right">
                                    <placeName>
                                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-11-15">November 15,
                                        1940</date>.</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to the Department’s
                                instruction of this date<note n="91" xml:id="d695fn91">Not
                                    printed.</note> by which you were directed to return to your
                                post at Vichy, you are now instructed, after your return to your
                                post, to proceed to North Africa and to such other areas as may be
                                necessary to carry out instructions which have been given you
                                verbally.</p>
                            <p>[Here follows transportation authorization, etc.]</p>
                            <p>Very truly yours,</p>
                            <closer>For the Secretary of State: <lb/>
                                <signed>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Breckinridge Long</hi>
                                </signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>